flowchart TD

    %% Core User Flow
    U[User] -->|owns| O[Organization]
    U -->|has| BA[Bank Account]
    U -->|defines| B[Budget]
    U -->|generates| AL[Audit Log]

    %% Bank Account & Transactions
    BA -->|contains| T[Transaction]

    %% Transaction Relations
    T -->|related to| M[Merchant]
    T -->|classified as| C[Category]
    T -->|tagged via| TT[Transaction_Tags]
    TT -->|references| TG[Tag]

    %% Category Hierarchy
    C -->|parent of| C2[Category Parent]

    %% Budgets
    B -->|applies to| C

    %% Recurring Rules
    M -->|defines| RR[Recurring Rule]

    %% Audit
    AL -->|tracks entity| E[Entity Transaction/Budget/etc.]